{"scenicName": "故宫", "city": "北京", "scenes": [{"text": "哎呀，各位朋友们好呀！我是红魔馆的门卫红美铃，今天带大家去个好地方！", "expression": "happy3", "audioFile": "seg-00.mp3", "durationInFrames": 209, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "咱们今天要逛的，就是大名鼎鼎的北京故宫，世界最大的木结构宫殿群呢！", "expression": "happy_confident", "audioFile": "seg-01.mp3", "durationInFrames": 192, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "它可是明清两代24位皇帝住过的地方，有六百多年历史啦！", "expression": "excited", "audioFile": "seg-02.mp3", "durationInFrames": 169, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "故宫坐落在北京的正中心，沿着中轴线对称排开，气派非凡哦！", "expression": "default", "audioFile": "seg-03.mp3", "durationInFrames": 182, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "整个紫禁城占地72万平方米，光房屋就有九千多间，走三天都看不完！", "expression": "surprised", "audioFile": "seg-04.mp3", "durationInFrames": 216, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "这儿四季分明，春天百花盛开，秋天银杏金黄，是游览的最佳时节。", "expression": "happy3", "audioFile": "seg-05.mp3", "durationInFrames": 204, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "说起它的历史，那是明朝永乐皇帝在1420年建成的，到现在刚好六百年出头呢。", "expression": "thinking", "audioFile": "seg-06.mp3", "durationInFrames": 235, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "古人认为天帝住紫微宫，皇帝是天子，禁百姓入内，所以叫紫禁城。", "expression": "thinking", "audioFile": "seg-07.mp3", "durationInFrames": 212, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "这里发生过太多大事了，明朝壬寅宫变、清朝朝政，还有溥仪离宫。", "expression": "thinking", "audioFile": "seg-08.mp3", "durationInFrames": 196, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "到1925年，紫禁城改名为故宫博物院，正式向老百姓开放，咱们才能进去参观哟！", "expression": "happy_confident", "audioFile": "seg-09.mp3", "durationInFrames": 222, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "走过午门，迎面就是恢弘的太和殿，那是皇帝举行大典的地方。", "expression": "excited", "audioFile": "seg-10.mp3", "durationInFrames": 179, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "太和殿高约35米，汉白玉台阶刻着云龙纹，庄严又华丽！", "expression": "surprised", "audioFile": "seg-11.mp3", "durationInFrames": 184, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "乾清宫是皇帝的寝宫，正大光明匾后藏着立储的秘密呢。", "expression": "confused", "audioFile": "seg-12.mp3", "durationInFrames": 171, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "御花园里古树参天，堆秀山上的御景亭适合赏花看景。", "expression": "happy3", "audioFile": "seg-13.mp3", "durationInFrames": 166, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "别忘了东六宫的珍宝馆，乾隆皇帝的龙袍发簪，金光闪闪的！", "expression": "excited", "audioFile": "seg-14.mp3", "durationInFrames": 175, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "宫墙外的角楼，九梁十八柱七十二脊，造型精巧极了。", "expression": "happy3", "audioFile": "seg-15.mp3", "durationInFrames": 162, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "故宫在1987年成为世界文化遗产，建筑技术举世无双。", "expression": "confident", "audioFile": "seg-16.mp3", "durationInFrames": 178, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "这里藏着超180万件文物，从青铜器到书画，全是国之瑰宝。", "expression": "happy_confident", "audioFile": "seg-17.mp3", "durationInFrames": 196, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "它不只是一座宫殿，更是中华文明浓缩的精华，值得细细品味。", "expression": "thinking", "audioFile": "seg-18.mp3", "durationInFrames": 178, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "想去故宫玩，最好选春秋两季，天气舒适，游客也少。", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-19.mp3", "durationInFrames": 167, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "推荐上午走中轴线看三大殿，下午逛西六宫和珍宝馆。", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-20.mp3", "durationInFrames": 168, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "记得提前在官网预约门票哦，带上身份证，穿双舒服的鞋子！", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-21.mp3", "durationInFrames": 164, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "怎么样，故宫是不是超有魅力？每一次来都有新惊喜。", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-22.mp3", "durationInFrames": 168, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "希望大家能亲自感受这份历史的厚重，我红美铃在这里等着大家！", "expression": "confident", "audioFile": "seg-23.mp3", "durationInFrames": 179, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "那就先这样啦，咱们下次再一起去别的好地方玩，拜拜！", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-24.mp3", "durationInFrames": 151, "imageFile": "vid_1c77f878bb97-img-00.jpg"}], "totalFrames": 4713}